  <div class="project-grid">
    <div class="project-card">
      <h3>Rails Shopwise</h3>
      <p>A feature-rich e-commerce app built with Ruby on Rails. Includes product browsing, shopping cart, and admin panel.</p>
      <div class="project-links">
